  global process
  audio = ""
  for i in args:
    audio += str(i)
  audio = audio.replace('"', "")
  audio = audio.replace('*', "dash ")
  with open("Database//Speak//Speak.txt", "w") as file:
    file.write(audio)
    process = subprocess.Popen(["python", "Utils//RunTTS.py"])
